WEBVTT

00:00.602 --> 00:04.242
I'm in love. She's married.

00:06.475 --> 00:08.216
They're in the process of divorcing.

00:08.242 --> 00:11.221
But since I can't marry
a divorcee, it makes no odds.

00:12.922 --> 00:18.202
The Church sees the love
I have for her as shameful,

00:18.702 --> 00:20.014
as wrong.

00:21.286 --> 00:25.219
But if God is love, how can it be?

00:25.965 --> 00:29.200
You told me to put duty
above my own needs,

00:29.240 --> 00:30.874
above everything else.

00:31.053 --> 00:35.254
For what? An institution that
cares more about rules

00:35.280 --> 00:36.806
than it does about people?

00:36.960 --> 00:39.256
I can't do it any more.

00:39.834 --> 00:41.259
You've lost your faith.

00:41.285 --> 00:43.445
I have lost my faith in the Church.

00:47.330 --> 00:50.655
When I hear it speak,
I don't hear God any more.

00:53.366 --> 00:55.132
There's nothing I can say, is there?

00:57.217 --> 00:59.137
I will stay until you find
a replacement.

00:59.163 --> 01:01.363
But I would like to tender
my resignation.

01:05.750 --> 01:07.729
Write a letter of notice to the bishop.

01:08.383 --> 01:09.901
Once we receive it...

01:10.836 --> 01:12.316
..you can leave.

01:18.295 --> 01:20.387
I nearly left once.

01:21.246 --> 01:25.340
Then I remembered what's so
beautiful about what we do.

01:25.559 --> 01:29.185
It's the solace we provide
sitting by someone's side.

01:29.375 --> 01:32.983
No words needed. Just being
with them is enough.

01:33.627 --> 01:35.542
Talk to God.

01:37.160 --> 01:39.920
He's the only one who can guide you now.

